Albert Salmi https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Albert_Salmi 0 Albert Salmi (March 11, 1928 – April 22, 1990) was an American actor of stage, film, and television. He was noted as a character actor and appeared in over 150 film and television productions. Albert_Salmi ( March_11_,_1928 – April_22_,_1990 ) was an_American_actor of stage , film , and television .
